data.description: You do not want to miss this beautiful brick home, on a level lot with a nice porch to sit with family and friends to entertain. The space in the home has a oversized family room and a dinning area as well, recently renovated completely. The main room has some great updated features that will allow you to feel the relaxation of enjoying this peaceful home. You do not want to miss this opportunity to view this beauty. Call today for a showing and turn this house into a home before the holidays...
